data.description: Under contract-accepting backup offers. Back on the market, buyers financing fell through. Welcome to your dream home on the shores of tranquility! This stunning lakefront property offers you an unrivaled experience with breathtaking views that will leave you speechless. The 2394 sq. ft. Lennar-built masterpiece boasts 5 bedrooms, 3.5 baths, and an open great room, designed for a life of luxury. You won't be able to take your eyes off the water view that bathes the home in natural light.  The kitchen, a true chef's haven, features tall 42” cabinets, stainless steel appliances, and gleaming granite countertops, making meal preparation a delight. The spacious DOWNSTAIRS MASTER BEDROOM with its own master bath, complete with a walk-in shower, is a serene retreat you'll love coming home to. And oh, don't forget to check out the Master Closet – it's a "WOW" moment!  Step outside to your newly landscaped front yard and enjoy the screened-in covered lanai, perfect for sipping your morning coffee or hosting a lakeside soiree. This is an amazing home offering a great value at a Great price.   This is not just a home; it's a lifestyle in a gated community called Hawks Point. Here, you'll have access to a community pool, fitness center, playground, and a fully fenced dog park. There's also an expansive recreation area with a clubhouse, pool, outdoor kitchen, playground, and a large outdoor covered area overlooking the dog park  This home exudes pride of ownership and is free from any flood zone concerns. With a LOW HOA fee and quick access to I-75, Hawks Point is a gem of a community offering resort-style amenities, and it's just a stone's throw away from shopping, dining, golf, schools, and hospitals. Enjoy the convenience of downtown Tampa and the beaches with ease!  Don't miss out on this EXCEPTIONAL HOME at an extraordinary value – make it yours today!**** All Information Is Deemed Accurate - Buyer and Buyer's Agent to verify. ****
